-03-10T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>見到隔離post講開兒童色情，諗落又對呢類法例認知好矇糊，淨係知唔可以管有<br />\n<br />\n咁如果淨係上網睇呢類相，影片之類，睇完就熄左佢，過程中同埋事後都冇作任何download嘅行為，咁算唔算犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 純粹學術討論，冇諗過亦未曾以身試法</blockquote><br />\n睇己經load左喺你電腦cache/temp folder?</blockquote><br />\n我意思係係人地張貼嘅網站睇wo<br />\n<br />\n本身對電腦唔熟，如果就你所講，即係我地平時上網睇到嘅媒體都算download左？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9350e4e0787d480c5b2736ce602a72b8588917d2","tid":150704,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:16:39.000Z","msg":"要入你<br />\n有cache好似照入到"},{"pid":"bcbddfabb9c14d107207486495a065e58ae448fe","tid":150704,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:21:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要入你<br />\n有cache好似照入到</blockquote><br />\n即係電腦會自動將上網見到嘅媒體放入disk cache??<br />\n所以只要我地有開到張貼左兒童色情嘅網站，電腦就會將佢快取，所以就犯法？？<br />\n係唔係咁"},{"pid":"636d64611cfea12a20e81fbfd40ec697f84419ca","tid":150704,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:29:29.000Z","msg":"都係個個廢話<br />\n有心告你指甲銼都可以拉你<br />\n冇心告你攞關刀都冇人理你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過睇好似都犯法"},{"pid":"40749b1740dc318a16f836ca0f439f740d827f84","tid":150704,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"我諗係個官判斷你係唔小心，好奇定慣犯而判"},{"pid":"3fc8ef943ab14b8a42d4eb78cf294aa61f7b2b39","tid":150704,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T09:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗係個官判斷你係唔小心，好奇定慣犯而判</blockquote><br />\n關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家香港條